				<p><font size="1">Frequently Asked Questions</font></p><br>

				<h5><font color="white">Why can't I add to a story twice?</font></h5>
				<p><font size="2">Collaboration is the key to creativity.  That's why StoryShare only allows each user to contribute once to any particular story. </font></p>
				<br>
				<h5><font color="white">How can I find a story I've already added to?</font></h5>
				<p><font size="2">The search bar at the top of the page allows you to search for individual stories by title.</font></p>
				<br>
				<h5><font color="white">Why can't I add to stories listed in the Story Archive?</font>3</h5>
				<p><font size="2">StoryShare has a ten sentence limit for each story.  Once a story reaches ten sentences long, it can no longer be added to. But you can still read and enjoy it!</font></p>
